    <string name="setup_1_title">What this does</string>
    <string name="setup_1_body">This add-on puts an “Open in Stremio” button on your movies and episodes in SeriesGuide. Tap it, and Stremio opens on that exact title.</string>
    <string name="setup_2_title">Turn it on in SeriesGuide</string>
    <string name="setup_2_body">The button only appears after you switch the extension on inside SeriesGuide. Open Extensions and enable “Open in Stremio”.</string>
    <string name="setup_3_title">Make sure Stremio is installed</string>
    <string name="setup_3_body">The button opens the Stremio app, so it needs to be installed. If it isn’t on your device yet, grab it first — it’s free.</string>
    <string name="setup_4_title">You’re all set</string>
    <string name="setup_4_body">That’s it. Open any movie or episode in SeriesGuide and look for “Open in Stremio”.</string>
